Gaps</em>, LMU/Munich and Kings College London.</li>

<li>CIW (Coalition of Immokalee Workers), 2010,
 &ldquo;<a href="http://www.ciw-online.org/Resources/tools/general/10Slavery%20in%20the%20Fields.pdf" target="other">Slavery in the Fields and the Food We Eat</a>&rdquo;.</li>
 
<li>Kaplan, David,
 <a href="http://www.food.unt.edu/" target="other">Philosophy of Food Project</a>,
 University of North Texas</li>

<li>Mood, A. and P. Brooke, 2010,
 &ldquo;<a href="http://fishcount.org.uk/published/std/fishcountstudy.pdf" target="other">Estimating the Number of Fish Caught in Global Fishing Each Year</a>&rdquo;,
 at fishcount.org.uk.</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 2012,
 &ldquo;<a href="http://fishcount.org.uk/published/std/fishcountstudy2.pdf" target="other">Estimating the Number of Farmed Fish Killed in Global Aquaculture Each Year</a>&rdquo;,
 at fishcount.org.uk.</li>

<li>Ritchie, H., P. Rosado, and M. Roser, 2023,
 &ldquo;<a href="https://ourworldindata.org/animal-welfare">Animal Welfare</a>&rdquo;,
 at https://ourworldindata.org.</li>
</ul>
</div>

